                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;The project is in an early Beta stage at present. You can (at least currently) activate axe selectors in your CSS styles by including &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;script src=&quot;https://rouninmedia.github.io/axe/axe.js&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; at the very end of your html document, just before &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;/body&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;

