            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Tyler CSS4 is being considered by those that maintain the spec.  Announcement link  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.w3.org/community/css4/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;w3.org/community/css4&lt;/a&gt; Discussion link  &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/4770&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/4770&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

